b947-e9a105cf3201,1782834023169/full/max/0/default.jpg?im=Crop%2Crect%3D%280%2C121%2C4714%2C2651%29%3BResize%3D620\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 0.75em;padding:5px 10px;background:#f0f4f8;border-left:3px solid #7b9fc4;border-radius:3px;font-size:0.82em;color:#444;line-height:1.8;\">🔧 🪶 <a href=\"https://zirnhelt.github.io/super-rss-feed/review.html?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fentertainment%2Fcarl-rinsch-netflix-sentenced-white-horse-9.7254028%3Fcmp%3Drss\" style=\"color:#7b9fc4;text-decoration:none;\">✏️</a></p>\n<img src=\"https://i.cbc.ca/ais/7fd7612b-8058-4921-b947-e9a105cf3201,1782834023169/full/max/0/default.jpg?im=Crop%2Crect%3D%280%2C121%2C4714%2C2651%29%3BResize%3D620\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 0.75em;padding:5px 10px;background:#f0f4f8;border-left:3px solid #7b9fc4;border-radius:3px;font-size:0.82em;color:#444;line-height:1.8;\">🔧 🪶 <a href=\"https://zirnhelt.github.io/super-rss-feed/review.html?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fentertainment%2Fcarl-rinsch-netflix-sentenced-white-horse-9.7254028%3Fcmp%3Drss\" style=\"color:#7b9fc4;text-decoration:none;\">✏️</a></p>\n<img alt=\"A man in a blue suit walks down a street.\" height=\"349\" src=\"https://i.cbc.ca/ais/7fd7612b-8058-4921-b947-e9a105cf3201,1782834023169/full/max/0/default.jpg?im=Crop%2Crect%3D%280%2C121%2C4714%2C2651%29%3BResize%3D%28620%29\" title=\"Carl Rinsch leaves a federal courthouse in New York, Monday, June 29, 2026.\" width=\"620\" /><p>Hollywood writer-director Carl Rinsch was sentenced Monday to two-and-half-years in prison after being convicted of defrauding Netflix out of $11 million US for a never-finished sci-fi series. Supporters including Keanu Reeves had asked the court to show leniency.</p>",
